# No environment secrets are required to run the API.
#
# - Write auth uses per-user API keys stored in Firestore (apiKeys/{hash}),
#   minted via POST /v1/keys; there is no shared key to configure.
# - In production the Admin SDK auto-detects the project; the Firestore emulator
#   host is set by the test harness for local tests.
#
# (The old AUTOLOOP_WRITE_KEYS shared key was removed in Sub-project B.)
